                    "text": "<p>Java has been around for a long time but it still continues to be among the most popular programming languages. It is definitely a language that beginners in web development and app development should master. Besides giving you a solid foundation to master other object oriented concept and languages, it also gives your resume a good standing. <a href=\"https://www.monster.com/career-advice/article/highest-paying-skills-java-developer-jobs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Java programmers can earn upto $106,610 per year while senior developers can earn upto 139,132 per year.&nbsp;</a></p><p>This workshop will help you master Java with its thorough course outline and experiential format. Enrol now.&nbsp;</p>"
